Notifications
FOR OFFLINE APPLICATION

* Notes :
• Read all the Instructions carefully first.
• After that, click on the "I have read and accepted the above instructions carefully" checkbox.
• Then,Continue button will appear. Now,click on Continue Button.
• It will redirect to Verification Page.Then, Verify your Phone and Aadhaar.
• Once Verified, you can fill up the form. If you already applied, you will not be allowed to apply again.
• In order to make change to your previous application,click on CHANGE REGISTRATION.You need to upload your PHOTO,AADHAAR COPY,INCOME COPY and SIGNATURE again.
Shri N. Biren Singh Honourable Chief Minister, Manipur.

GENERAL INSTRUCTION FOR FORM FILL-UP

• One Applicant can apply once.
• Applicant should enclosed his/her photo copy in Jpeg/png format.
• Aadhaar number is compulsary for the applicant.
• Scan copy of the aadhaar in PDF format for the applicant should be enclosed.
• Scan copy of the Income certificate in PDF format issued by DC/SDO/SDC should be enclosed.
• Photo Copy of the signature in Jpeg/Png is mandatory.
• Aadhaar copy,Income certificate copy should be in PDF format and maximum size of 400kb.
• Signature photo,Applicant's photo should be in JPEG/PNG format and maximum size of 400kb.
• After the completion of form fill-up,a copy of the details can be printed.
• Once applied,you can check the status in the CHECK MY STATUS button above by entering the registered mobile number and Aadhaar No.
